    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/67531886983aaac5b35f3de2f9556680.poster.avif?t=1663081168\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/67531886983aaac5b35f3de2f9556680.webm?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/67531886983aaac5b35f3de2f9556680.mp4?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>冲突<br>在叙利亚的沙漠边际处，处处可见破碎阿勒珀的废墟颓垣断壁。曾经的辉煌早已在军事冲突中化为灰烬。空气中弥漫着恐惧、紧张和不安，每个角落都有危险的味道。这就是战争。没有食物，没有水，只有帐篷可做遮蔽。没有朋友或支援，只有敌人和恶意。为生存而战，无论结果如何，你只有一个目标：活下去！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/1b3cc7ff2aadaec1f8f98ee6c2974509.poster.avif?t=1663081168\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/1b3cc7ff2aadaec1f8f98ee6c2974509.webm?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/1b3cc7ff2aadaec1f8f98ee6c2974509.mp4?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏<br>你是行走在阿勒珀城市废墟中的一名勇敢工兵，负责在危机四伏的环境中进行排雷，这绝非易事。没有任何安全地带，你必须时刻保持警惕，因为恐怖分子制造的简易炸弹几乎比比皆是，可能隐藏在自行车、罐头或者门框中，走错一步就可能导致炸弹。百姓随时都面临生命危险，保护他们是您的使命。敌人可能发动突袭，在他们面前你如此势单力薄。一切都远非看上去的样子，你必须保持专注，努力挽救尽可能多的生命。压力重重，时间紧迫。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/3c2b0d7e28ff67e70e4690106ce5e20a.poster.avif?t=1663081168\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/3c2b0d7e28ff67e70e4690106ce5e20a.webm?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/3c2b0d7e28ff67e70e4690106ce5e20a.mp4?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>现实故事<br>这款游戏以一场真实的军事冲突为背景。在连绵不绝的战火中，曾经富朔宏伟的阿勒珀早已变得满目苍夷。百姓生命危在旦夕，眼前的一切都将灰飞烟灭。问题越来越困难，压力几乎达到崩溃边缘。在如此逼真的画面中，你仿佛真正置身于叙利亚沙漠的边缘地带，百姓的生命就掌握在你的手中，你的每一步都将决定全局走向。在如此紧迫的时间中，你会做出怎样的决定？并非所有炸弹都可以顺利拆除。你会直面那近乎不可能的选择吗？你会选择拯救谁？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/1d92fc38996e7496c688bffe20cc6ccd.poster.avif?t=1663081168\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/1d92fc38996e7496c688bffe20cc6ccd.webm?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/1d92fc38996e7496c688bffe20cc6ccd.mp4?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>合作成果<br>本游戏在开发之初，就获得了军事专家的大力支持，尽可能准确地反映现实。在制作游戏的过程中，我们与C-IED（反简易爆炸装置）专家密切合作，了解制造和拆卸炸弹的知识。此外，我们还与波兰雷霆特种部队相关领域的军官合作，在技术活动和虚拟战场情景方面获得帮助。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/0f45971e6cf3fe518dc8951a018b0833.poster.avif?t=1663081168\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/0f45971e6cf3fe518dc8951a018b0833.webm?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/0f45971e6cf3fe518dc8951a018b0833.mp4?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏特点<br>在虚拟工兵游戏中，您可以：<br>拆除恐怖分子制造的简易炸弹<br>控制拆弹机器人和专业金属探测器<br>在最不起眼的地点和物体上搜索炸弹，<br>每次任务中拯救平民可获得额外积分<br>提高你的技能和等级，积累更多资源，但拆弹失败会给你带来损失<br>想要获得成功，你必须：<br>与其他士兵密切合作，毕竟你在战场中进行的是团队行动<br>做出可影响百姓生命的艰难决定：比如是进行拆弹，还是从外围入手，将炸药转移到安全地点<br>应对压力。时间迫在眉睫，你的技能、精确度和所选择的方法对百姓而言生死攸关。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/f57863f4e4fd23b2d9a20eb0ad1187b5.poster.avif?t=1663081168\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/f57863f4e4fd23b2d9a20eb0ad1187b5.webm?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455580/extras/f57863f4e4fd23b2d9a20eb0ad1187b5.mp4?t=1663081168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
